high_descs: Step forward to face the kitchen table.
Pick up the knife on the kitchen table.
Turn right and walk across the room to face the tomato on the end of the counter.
Cut the tomato on the end of the counter into slices.
Turn left and walk across the room, then turn left to face the trash can.
Place the knife in the trash can.
Walk back across the room to face the tomato on the end of the counter.
Pick up the tomato slice on the end of the counter.
Walk around the counter and turn right to face the microwave.
Heat the tomato slice in the microwave and then remove it.
Turn around and walk across the room and turn left to face the trash can.
Place the tomato slice in the trash can.
anns.task_desc: To put a heated slice of tomato in the trash can.

high_descs: Move a step forward to the white table
Pick up a butter knife from the table
Turn to your right, take a few steps, turn left to go across the room, turn left to face the counter with a tomato
Cut the tomato into slices
Turn to your left with the knife, move across the room and turn left toward the counter with a bin below the counter
Put the knife in the bin
Go back to the counter with the sliced tomato
Pick up the front slice of tomato from the counter
Take the tomato slice and go to the stove
Put the slice on the stove to warm it and pick it up
Go back to the counter with the bin below it
Put the tomato slice in the bin
anns.task_desc: To put a heated slice of tomato in a bin

high_descs: Turn and go to the round table.
Pick up a knife on the round table.
Turn and go to the counter by the stove.
Cut the tomato on the counter by the stove.
Turn and go to the trash can.
Put the knife in the trash can.
Turn and go to the counter by the stove.
Pick up a slice of tomato on the counter.
Turn and go to the microwave.
Heat the slice of tomato in the microwave.
Turn and go to the trash can.
Put the slice of tomato in the trash can.
anns.task_desc: Put a microwaved slice of tomato in the trash can.
